api_spec_excerpt:
POST /v1/notifications/bulk
Body: { template_id: string, recipient_ids: string[] (max 100000), schedule_at: datetime }
Response: { campaign_id: string, recipient_count: integer, estimated_completion: datetime }

GET /v1/search?q={query}
Response: { results: [ { id, title, relevance_score: float } ] }
Note: relevance_score definition TBD pending ranking model decision.

GET /v1/export/data
Headers: X-RateLimit-Limit: 10, X-RateLimit-Remaining: integer, X-RateLimit-Reset: unix_timestamp
Error 429: { error: 'rate_limit_exceeded', retry_after: integer }

POST /v1/subscriptions/{id}/downgrade
Response: { new_tier: string, prorated_credit: decimal, credit_applied_to_invoice: string }
Note: Annual subscription downgrades return credit: 0 (known limitation).
